<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<refentry xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xml:id="tbxInstall" xml:lang="en">
    <refnamediv>
        <refname>tbxInstall</refname>
        <refpurpose>install a toolbox from git and enable it</refpurpose>
    </refnamediv>
    <refsynopsisdiv>
        <title>Syntax</title>
        <synopsis>
tbxInstall(name)
tbxInstall(name, source)
        </synopsis>
    </refsynopsisdiv>
    <refsection>
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>Resolves <literal>name</literal> to a toolbox source, clones or pulls it, builds it, registers it in the manifest with autoload enabled, and loads it. <literal>source</literal> is <literal>"local"</literal> (use <literal>~/Projects/SciLabProjects/&lt;name&gt;</literal>), <literal>"remote"</literal> (clone from <literal>jlmoya</literal> on GitLab then GitHub), or omitted (prefer a local clone, else remote).</para>
    </refsection>
    <refsection>
        <title>Examples</title>
        <programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
tbxInstall("cgal");
tbxInstall("sndfile-toolbox", "remote");
]]></programlisting>
    </refsection>
